{"tid":1250623,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"手機學徙，你問我答 （大範圍版）","createTime":"2019-06-22T06:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T18:04:03.000Z","uid":236206,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f3be49b8523b85447b193efe293e8a35e62007","tid":1250623,"uid":236206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"手機學徙你問我答<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市面好多唔同課程，都可以講下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有咩問題都可以問下</span></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有無初學者想成為手機維修師父，有嘅可以聯絡我<br />\n<br />\n教授課程<br />\n<br />\nCore部分係必修****<br />\n包括手機結構，平板結構<br />\n裝拆，理論<br />\n檢查，基本維修<br />\n<br />\n之後分兩part，自選<br />\n<br />\n1）液晶維修<br />\n<br />\n不單單係裝隻mon上去<br />\n而係從理論開始<br />\n教你由結構開始<br />\n<br />\nLCD與LED維修的分別<br />\n做落嘅細節<br />\n如何將液晶分離，清潔，重新打做成一隻新顯示模組（直面mon, 曲面mon) <br />\n如何重新壓排線<br />\n修復<br />\n<br />\n2）主機板維修<br />\n<br />\n由理論，電路結構教起<br />\n到電路圖紙，檢查<br />\n再拆焊，植焊<br />\n最後裝回晶片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學完更有機會於我工場其下工作<br />\n人工可達16-20k<br />\n<br />\n有意請 <a href=\"https://t.me/fixmm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffixmm&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2BhxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c143a20f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fixmm</a><br />\n</span><br />\n只要露兩手，便知質素有沒有"},{"pid":"27c36fa8d36e5229a61114d34926408bf978d1e0","tid":1250623,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要換幾多個mon先有16k"},{"pid":"48d4ebe8179d667cd2c13b679dc7a4b110299ced","tid":1250623,"uid":236206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27c36fa8d36e5229a61114d34926408bf978d1e0","tid":1250623,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:05:43.000Z"